{"tid":1366074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"改裝交通標誌路牌做盾","createTime":"2019-07-26T00:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T16:48:22.000Z","uid":271284,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f91fd81b675a67be3efc1a2871b6881712e1d079","tid":1366074,"uid":271284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:31:01.000Z","msg":"動漫節又到，我想cosplay Brad Pitt呢個造型<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8dPGt3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8dPGt3.png&h=0a9b55e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個盾同街邊路牌差唔多size，用來改裝就啱曬，但拆街邊路牌犯法既，可以去淘寶買就唔犯法<br />\n路牌前面有兩個洞，正常用來上螺絲既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01PfBYu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01PfBYu.png&h=7d0e75eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n響個洞度穿條索帶過去，再響第二邊上粒螺絲帽，條索帶就會固定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oo6hQm2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foo6hQm2.png&h=f6f8b36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krvqZci.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrvqZci.png&h=c1c9789a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再噴黑塊路牌就真係成個Brad Pitt咁型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eEVFLeX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeEVFLeX.png&h=79f598cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩開cosplay都知cosplayer最煩兩樣野，第一就係裝備好貴。咁樣改裝個盾就超平<br />\n<br />\n第二就係未到會場之前變裝，響街度比人見到真係會好柒。呢個方法咁簡單，可以去到會場先整，就唔怕響條街度出醜啦"},{"pid":"2423a209a01b8cdc2992df057120993947322491","tid":1366074,"uid":80303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ayo0LYi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fayo0LYi.png&h=e3efb703&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f394237faa0f600dd4f27753706319714c41a70d","tid":1366074,"uid":264915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362bb949a3edc36dd9e54dba3f57e490f032ba0b","tid":1366074,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a8e567f5068e1abf9385277c6f5da6a77aff127","tid":1366074,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:34:56.000Z","msg":"加塊海棉拖住仲正"},{"pid":"e937b9186ab92e7082eeca79ddecf90005661df1","tid":1366074,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:34:56.000Z","msg":"727元朗捉精靈"},{"pid":"76e6c1a12d7769ae649346d51582f7fd39636b47","tid":1366074,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:36:19.000Z","msg":"726機場見<br />\n727元朗捉精靈"},{"pid":"9b397318d455c4cf48ddc921097a35e179b7f4c1","tid":1366074,"uid":140233,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:36:30.000Z","msg":"咪撚拆Stop sign"},{"pid":"f55d2f9ba069b2f209cda6647312903906ebcaf1","tid":1366074,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:36:40.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"cc3a8ff04ff3f658b2b2d1ec8698b8402d4bf055","tid":1366074,"uid":41611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c185c8d4530f4ead5425cab6321e9a393cd4e936","tid":1366074,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21119827e2301b4b0f00d633b40fbb9f4711d79a","tid":1366074,"uid":52605,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:39:07.000Z","msg":"提示：交通標誌好多前朝遺物  仲用緊舊字體 <br />\n呢啲拆一個就少一個<br />\n唔好拆呢啲啦<br />\n<br />\n要用自己買